dnl AC_CHECK_FUNCS(scm_from_ulong)
AC_CHECK_FUNCS(scm_num2ulong)
AC_CHECK_FUNCS(gh_scm2ulong) dnl from 1.6 API
dnl the following are in guile-1.8, but not earlier
AC_CHECK_FUNCS(scm_is_bool)
